      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikidata"
    },
    {
      "text": "Paws and Claws: Pet Vet is a pet-raising simulation video game by German studio Radon Labs in which players can nurse dogs, cats, horses, birds, hamsters, guinea pigs and rabbits back to health. The game features 20 ailments. Players can design their own clinic, choose which kennels to build and expand existing buildings to provide further services to their patients.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "Paws and Claws Pet Vet è un videogioco di simulazione di una clinica per animali sviluppato da Radon Labs e pubblicato da DTP Entertainment per Microsoft Windows nel 2005 e da THQ nel 2007 per Nintendo DS.",
      "lang": "it",
      "source": "wikipedia_it"
    },
    {
      "text": "『Paws and Claws: Pet Vet』は、ドイツのスタジオRadon Labsが開発したペット育成シミュレーションビデオゲームです。プレイヤーは、犬、猫、馬、鳥、ハムスター、モルモット、ウサギなどの動物たちを治療し、健康に回復させていきます。本作には20種類もの病気が登場します。プレイヤーは自分だけのクリニックを設計したり、ケージを建設したり、既存の建物を拡張したりして、患者たちにより多くのサービスを提供することができます。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "ai_local_gemma4",
      "base_lang": "en"
    }
  ]
